snippet.title: The Sims 3 Showtime | Katy Perry Collector's Edition Trailer
snippet.description:
Katy Perry joins creative forces with The Sims, kicking off with a Katy Perry-themed Collector's Edition for The Sims 3 Showtime. 

Rise to fame in The Sims™ 3 Showtime Katy Perry Collector's Edition that includes downloadable content including an Ultimate Stage bonus venue, iconic Katy Perry themed items, and an exclusive poster. 

This iconic content includes fashions, a guitar, a hairstyle and various Katy Perry themed stage props.
